Deutsche Bank May Announce Succession Plan This Week, Financial Times Says

-- B y   N a m i t h a   J a g a d e e s h
-- 
2011-07-25T00:55:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-25/deutsche-bank-may-announce-succession-plan-this-week-ft-says.html
Deutsche Bank AG (DBK)  may announce its
plan for a successor to Chief Executive Officer  Josef Ackermann 
this week, the Financial Times reported, citing a person
familiar with the bank.  It is “untenable” for the bank to delay the plan further,
the person said, according to the FT. 